title: OR: 11/18/13
author: UnknownOreo1996
pages:
#- The Oreo Report
11/18/13
-------------------November 18th, 2013

This report will be notifying all citizens, readers, etc. of what we've currently done and pose a few questions.
Please note: Each page is an article.
#- Well done everyone! According to the CAI we are ranked as the 4th most active city! Let's aim for even higher next month. Jaghut kindly graphed our growth.





#- The Fellowship Militia is now under the command of General Eldoorn. His reddit username is /u/Eldoorn.

Also the Militia currently is recruiting, please enlist today!
#- Notable Criminals:

