Also watch for more!
#- RhaeStarShine has returned after her break, please welcome her back to Fellowship!
#- Our mumble channel is sorta (kinda) fixed though I can't get admin to work for anyone else in the channel and my powers are partially limited. I'm doing my best to fix it.
#- That's all for now folks, thanks for reading and replying!

End Report
